# SECTION 4: Structural Diagrams & Schematics

## 4.1 Flowchart: Matrix Addition Program

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Declare matrices A B C and variables m n i j]
    B --> C[Read dimensions m and n from user]
    C --> D[Loop i from 0 to m-1]
    D --> E[Loop j from 0 to n-1]
    E --> F[Read A i j]
    F --> G{j less than n}
    G -- Yes --> E
    G -- No --> H{i less than m}
    H -- Yes --> D
    H -- No --> I[Loop i from 0 to m-1]
    I --> J[Loop j from 0 to n-1]
    J --> K[Read B i j]
    K --> L{j less than n}
    L -- Yes --> J
    L -- No --> M{i less than m}
    M -- Yes --> I
    M -- No --> N[Loop i from 0 to m-1]
    N --> O[Loop j from 0 to n-1]
    O --> P[Compute C i j equals A i j plus B i j]
    P --> Q[Print C i j]
    Q --> R{j less than n}
    R -- Yes --> O
    R -- No --> S{i less than m}
    S -- Yes --> N
    S -- No --> T[Stop]
```

