        L1[Outer Loop: i from 0 to m-1] --> L2[Middle Loop: j from 0 to p-1]
        L2 --> L3[Inner Loop: k from 0 to n-1]
        L3 --> L4[Accumulate: C i j plus equals A i k times B k j]
