        M0[a 0 0] --> M1[a 0 1] --> M2[a 0 2] --> M3[a 1 0] --> M4[a 1 1] --> M5[a 1 2] --> M6[a 2 0] --> M7[a 2 1] --> M8[a 2 2]
    end

