## 4.4 Logical Architecture: Operation Selection Block

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START[User Input: Two Matrices A and B] --> DECIDE{Choose Operation}
    DECIDE -- Addition --> ADD[Add corresponding elements: C i j equals A i j plus B i j]
    DECIDE -- Subtraction --> SUB[Subtract: C i j equals A i j minus B i j]
    DECIDE -- Multiplication --> MUL[Triple loop dot product]
    DECIDE -- Transpose --> TR[Swap indices: T j i equals A i j]
