### Question B (14 Marks) — ALTERNATIVE CHOICE

**`[KTU University Exam - Dec 2024]`**

**(a) [7 marks]** Explain the concept of an **array of structures** in C with a suitable example. Write a program to read and display the records of 5 employees (with fields: id, name, salary).

**(b) [7 marks]** Explain the two ways of passing a structure to a function (by value and by address) with a suitable program. Justify which method is preferred for large structures.

